[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 3.0,
    "text": "Are you going to confront Penny?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.0,
    "endTime": 5.0,
    "text": "Eventually, I guess."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.0,
    "endTime": 10.0,
    "text": "Although I am kind of curious how long she thinks she can keep hiding my stuff without me knowing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.0,
    "endTime": 11.0,
    "text": "Hmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.0,
    "endTime": 17.0,
    "text": "Perhaps instead of confronting them, we should see how far they're willing to spin their tangled webs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.0,
    "endTime": 21.0,
    "text": "Like that Spider-Man action figure that used to be on your desk."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.0,
    "endTime": 23.0,
    "text": "Oh my god, I'm going blind."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.0,
    "endTime": 27.0,
    "text": "Hi!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.0,
    "endTime": 28.0,
    "text": "Food's here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.0,
    "endTime": 30.0,
    "text": "Excellent!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.0,
    "endTime": 32.0,
    "text": "I'm very hungry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.0,
    "endTime": 35.0,
    "text": "Speaking of which, what's going on with your apartment?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.0,
    "endTime": 40.0,
    "text": "Oh, uh, they're still working on it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.0,
    "endTime": 40.0,
    "text": "Interesting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.0,
    "endTime": 47.0,
    "text": "Very interesting. Yeah, we swung by her apartment on the way to the restaurant."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.0,
    "endTime": 48.0,
    "text": "They're going to be fixing it for a while."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.0,
    "endTime": 52.0,
    "text": "Wait, you saw her apartment?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.0,
    "endTime": 53.0,
    "text": "I did!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.0,
    "endTime": 58.0,
    "text": "Still a mess."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.0,
    "endTime": 59.0,
    "text": "Leonard?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "Yeah?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.0,
    "endTime": 63.0,
    "text": "G-Y-R-S-H-B."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.0,
    "endTime": 69.0,
    "text": "D-A-H-N-E-B-A-P-P-E-N-N-Y."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.0,
    "endTime": 72.0,
    "text": "That's a B."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.0,
    "endTime": 76.0,
    "text": "Why are you speaking Klingon?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.0,
    "endTime": 79.0,
    "text": "Why are you speaking English?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.0,
    "endTime": 82.0,
    "text": "This is ridiculous."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.0,
    "endTime": 84.0,
    "text": "Penny, do you remember when I taught you W-B-W?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.0,
    "endTime": 86.0,
    "text": "A bab's a bull, a bootlebee'd a bite-a-boo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.0,
    "endTime": 90.0,
    "text": "A beg's a bell-a-bird."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.0,
    "endTime": 94.0,
    "text": "A buzz's a bell-a-bim, a bow a bime-a-bye-a-bing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.0,
    "endTime": 97.0,
    "text": "A bith's a la-bem-a-da-bird-a-bull-a-bim."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.0,
    "endTime": 100.0,
    "text": "A bit's a pas-a-bib-a-bull."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.0,
    "endTime": 103.0,
    "text": "All right, now stop that!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.0,
    "endTime": 104.0,
    "text": "You stop that!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.0,
    "endTime": 107.0,
    "text": "D-Y-A-R-S-H-A."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.0,
    "endTime": 109.0,
    "text": "Koo-vah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.0,
    "endTime": 110.0,
    "text": "Okay, that's enough."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.0,
    "endTime": 111.0,
    "text": "You know what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.0,
    "endTime": 113.0,
    "text": "What is going on?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.0,
    "endTime": 121.0,
    "text": "Fine, I told Sheldon that her apartment's been finished, and you just said it's not, so now I'm all confused. Penny was just covering for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.0,
    "endTime": 124.0,
    "text": "My place has been ready for two weeks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.0,
    "endTime": 125.0,
    "text": "How could you lie to me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.0,
    "endTime": 127.0,
    "text": "She's enjoyed living with you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.0,
    "endTime": 128.0,
    "text": "It's called being in love."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.0,
    "endTime": 132.0,
    "text": "And what's it called when you secretly get rid of all your husband's stuff?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.0,
    "endTime": 134.0,
    "text": "Well, that is not true!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.0,
    "endTime": 135.0,
    "text": "Bernadette told Howard."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.0,
    "endTime": 136.0,
    "text": "Howard told me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.0,
    "endTime": 138.0,
    "text": "Plus, I can see all my stuff is gone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.0,
    "endTime": 143.0,
    "text": "Oh, so you believe your friend and your friend's wife in your own eyes over me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.0,
    "endTime": 147.0,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.0,
    "endTime": 156.0,
    "text": "You really didn't think I'd notice my stuff was missing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.0,
    "endTime": 158.0,
    "text": "Did you notice your keychain?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.0,
    "endTime": 169.0,
    "text": "Where's Batman? Hey, why did you tell Howard I was hiding Leonard's things?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.0,
    "endTime": 170.0,
    "text": "One sec."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.0,
    "endTime": 173.0,
    "text": "Why did you tell Leonard I told you Penny was hiding his things?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.0,
    "endTime": 179.0,
    "text": "It just came up, because we were talking about secrets, and..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.0,
    "endTime": 179.0,
    "text": "Wait."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.0,
    "endTime": 181.0,
    "text": "Would you stop it with that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.0,
    "endTime": 186.0,
    "text": "I'm not really a part of this, so I'm just gonna dig in."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.0,
    "endTime": 191.0,
    "text": "And I'd like to know why you blabbed about my apartment."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.0,
    "endTime": 195.0,
    "text": "You're up, blabby. Amy, I'm sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.0,
    "endTime": 197.0,
    "text": "I shouldn't have said anything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.0,
    "endTime": 199.0,
    "text": "I guess it's okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.0,
    "endTime": 204.0,
    "text": "I'm sorry that I lied about my apartment."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.0,
    "endTime": 205.0,
    "text": "It's alright."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.0,
    "endTime": 207.0,
    "text": "And?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.0,
    "endTime": 208.0,
    "text": "And what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.0,
    "endTime": 210.0,
    "text": "Your wizard robes are next to go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.0,
    "endTime": 216.0,
    "text": "Now that everything's out on the table, you think you two will keep living together?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.0,
    "endTime": 224.0,
    "text": "Despite recent events, I do consider our experiment in cohabitation to have been positive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.0,
    "endTime": 227.0,
    "text": "Are you saying you'd like to live with me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.0,
    "endTime": 230.0,
    "text": "I'm open to the possibility."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.0,
    "endTime": 232.0,
    "text": "Amy, but be Kabul."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.0,
    "endTime": 242.0,
    "text": "Whatever. You know, if he moves across the hall for good, Leonard could keep the stuff you don't like in Sheldon's old room."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.0,
    "endTime": 243.0,
    "text": "Solves everything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.0,
    "endTime": 244.0,
    "text": "That's a great idea!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.0,
    "endTime": 247.0,
    "text": "Ooh, maybe I could turn it into a gaming den."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.0,
    "endTime": 248.0,
    "text": "That would be amazing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.0,
    "endTime": 248.0,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.0,
    "endTime": 249.0,
    "text": "No, dude, what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.0,
    "endTime": 250.0,
    "text": "Excuse me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.0,
    "endTime": 251.0,
    "text": "That's my room."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.0,
    "endTime": 252.0,
    "text": "But you won't be living here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.0,
    "endTime": 254.0,
    "text": "But that's my room."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.0,
    "endTime": 254.0,
    "text": "But you won't be living here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.0,
    "endTime": 255.0,
    "text": "But that's my room."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.0,
    "endTime": 256.0,
    "text": "You guys might want to start eating."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.0,
    "endTime": 257.0,
    "text": "But you won't be living here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.0,
    "endTime": 262.0,
    "text": "Sweetie, once you stop paying rent, none of this is really yours."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.0,
    "endTime": 263.0,
    "text": "But that's my room."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.0,
    "endTime": 265.0,
    "text": " But you won't be living here!"
  }
]